Boutique-hotel "Achilles i Cherepakha" is located in the historical downtown of Saint-Petersburg close to the famous Dostoevsky's house. The hotel, located in the apartment building of the 19th century, is filled with the true spirit of Saint-Petersburg:&nbsp;you can feel it in&nbsp;every detail: from interior design to the peaceful blue sky seen from the windows. Classical interior of the hotel rooms allows you to dive into the atmosphere of the cultural capital, while dormer-windows and cozy courtyard remind the romance of Europe chamber hotels.&nbsp;<br>